msgctxt "talk04"
msgid ""
"<1.se_co><2.so><3.re_co>Yeah, I heard that you can make a\n"
"<4.se_co>cooling elixir <5.re_co>from <6.se_co>certain bugs and\n"
"monster materials<7.re_co>.\n"
"<8.so>But they don't sell the stuff anywhere,\n"
"and I'm a lousy cook.\n"
"\n"
"I hear the best place to find <9.se_co>bugs with\n"
"cooling effects<10.re_co> is in the <11.se_co>colder heights of\n"
"the Gerudo Highlands<12.re_co>.\n"
"But there are monsters there...\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<13.te_si><14.se_co>Too bad I'm allergic to monster "
"punches...<15.re_co><16.te_si>"
msgstr ""

